        <num>CC 1413</num>
        <heading>1413.  Prescription of action of rescission</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 1413.  Prescription of action of rescission.
Suits for the rescission of partitions are prescribed by the lapse of five years from the date thereof, and in case of error and fraud, from the day in which they are discovered.</p>
        </content>
